      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait u said i should adjust it based on how i feel? but like, if i'm feeling really fine and my monitor says i'm in range right now, is it totally fine to just skip the half dose and not take any at all? i just dont want to deal with a crash in the middle of the night if i didnt eat much.",
